                        p.text-white-50.mb-5
                            | I’ve worked across
                            strong.highlight a range of public and private sector clients
                            | , across a host of challenges - most notably behaviour change, brand strategy and comms development, audience understanding, customer experience and behavioural journey mapping. 
                        p.text-white-50.mb-5
                            | I bring 
                            strong.highlight applied behavioural science expertise
                            | across core frameworks (COM-B, B=MAP, context model) and a host of principles. I can support wider conversations through Bsci consultancy and workshops.
                        p.text-white-50.mb-5
                            | I have a wealth of experience across
                            strong.highlight qualitative methodologies
                            | - IDIs, paired depths, groups, observation, intercepts, online platforms, behavioural journeys/diaries, ethnography - running projects from foundational review and hypothesis development, to delivery of debriefs, workshops and co-creation sessions. My experience spans UK and International work, quick turnaround and longitudinal studies, and moderating a range of audiences across sensitive topics.

